title: Yo-yo mass manufacturing
short_description: Produced 200 identical yo-yos via injection molding for 2.008 (Design and Manufacturing II)
long_description: Produced 200 identical yo-yos for 2.008 (Design and Manufacturing II). The main bodies of the yo-yos were injection molded and carefully designed to press fit into each other. The molds were made by CNC milling. Although we didn't test the performance of the yo-yos, we measured the parts to ensure they were within tolerance.
